    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1902-10-13T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1902-10-13T00:00:00-05:00" n="878"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d878">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">His Majesty <persName type="from">Chulalongkorn</persName> to
                        President <persName type="to">Roosevelt</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Bangkok</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1902-10-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 13, 1902</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>I learned with pleasure the cordial reception you have kindly accorded to my son,
                    the Crown Prince, in your country. Pray accept my warmest thanks and the
                    assurance of my sincere friendship.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Chulalongkorn, R.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
